### Create a new game as white (engine moves second)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "side": "white"
}

###

### Create a new game as black (engine responds immediately)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "side": "black"
}

###

### Submit a move for an existing game (replace {{gameSlug}} with the game id like brave-rook-42)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/games/{{gameSlug}}/move
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "move": "e2e4"
}
